	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64752450"><p><div class="quote"><p>The COVID tests are unreliable, and doctors are still thrashing around blind trying to diagnose it</p></div><p>Which renders this discussion, about a globe-spanning pandemic with hundreds of millions of known positive cases in this country alone, totally absurd.</p><p>If with such high prevalence it still defies scientific analysis, I can only conclude that it does not exist as a physical disease. Perhaps a few people do get it bad, but the rest is just a collective delusion.</p></div>
